---
title: Tex-Mex Halloumi Tacos with Garlic Aioli & Zesty Slaw
description: Few things look as colourful as these tacos — with Tex-Mex halloumi inside no less! The real star of this dish is the creamy coleslaw. There’s crunch and a zesty hint amidst the expected tang of garlic aioli we all know and love, and all of that means you’re in for a burst of flavour.

